item.title: Hello World
item.description: Computer Security Roadmap Introductions Computer security is no longer a sacred art practiced by a few insular nerds, but rather a global issue where large teams work together to improve the privacy and safety of all. It is a constant arms race of finding chinks in the armour before those who would exploit them for personal gain. Here, in these blogs, and hopefully soon a youtube channel, I will explore the diverse field of security.

item.description: Loading ... import { Octokit } from "https://cdn.skypack.dev/@octokit/core"; const octokit = new Octokit(); (async function pullRepos(){ const excludedRepos = ["Angus-C-git", "insurance-management-system", "ipcalc", "freeCodeCamp", "first-contributions"]; const specials = ["LiveBreachTimeline"]; await octokit.request('GET /users/{username}/repos', { username: 'Angus-C-git', page: 1, per_page: 30 }).then(response = { let timeLine = document.getElementById("projects-timeline"); timeLine.innerText = ''; console.log(response.data) response.data.map(project = { console.log(project.html_url); if (!excludedRepos.includes(project.name)) timeLine.innerHTML += `${project.created_at.slice(0,7)} ${project.name} ${project.description} ` }); }); }());
